{"tid":264104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"16歲少女問路 遭4名南亞難民輪姦","createTime":"2017-05-30T14:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T23:51:43.000Z","uid":82646,"like":6,"dislike":96,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7a9909271ba64e9829712d3bf64a47da7fcad65a","tid":264104,"uid":82646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:20:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170527/56748753\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170527%2F56748753&d=zwaEkXe1hEW1tFfMBPrTd10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=0c4ba284\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170527%2F56748753&h=9c4f76a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170527/56748753</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/news/3662475/four-afghan-refugees-found-guilty-of-gang-raping-a-16-year-old-girl/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fnews%2F3662475%2Ffour-afghan-refugees-found-guilty-of-gang-raping-a-16-year-old-girl%2F&d=zwaEkXe1hEW1tFfMBPrTd10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=81f86ab1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thesun.co.uk/news/3662475/four-afghan-refugees-found-guilty-of-gang-raping-a-16-year-old-girl/</a><br />\n歐洲噩夢】16歲女問路遭輪姦 指4難民邊施暴邊笑淫淫<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/nintchdbpict000305696914-e1495840833279.jpg?strip=all&amp;w=626&amp;quality=100\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2Fnintchdbpict000305696914-e1495840833279.jpg%3Fstrip%3Dall%26w%3D626%26quality%3D100&h=f82e7072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRafiullah Hamidy, 24, found guilty of gang-raping a lost teen <br />\n<br />\n英國肯特郡4名阿富汗難民，輪姦一名向他們問路的16歲少女，受害人指4人邊施暴邊笑淫淫，她無力反抗，只可任由他們飽嚐獸慾。雖然4名難民否認強姦罪名，但陪審團裁定全部人罪名成立，法官將於7月判刑。<br />\n<br />\n事發在去年9月18日，4名被告由18至37歲不等，他們將喝醉酒並上前問路的16歲受害人，帶到位於中東烤肉店樓上、其中一名被告的家中輪姦。為免被受害人認出，眾人特意將燈關上。<br />\n受害人對陪審團表示：「我不肯定房內有多少人，我想4個或5個吧&hellip;&hellip;其中一人將我推倒在床上，他們都笑了，他們走過來時都在笑&hellip;&hellip;他們不停換人，他們在輪姦我。我叫他們停，但他們就是繼續。」<br />\n眾人飽嚐獸慾後將受害人送走，一名熱心女途人見她獨自在街上遊蕩飲泣，帶她回家並報警求助。"},{"pid":"dea1d275f79cb7f5b0be287b5e2eb9b16a1d05b0","tid":264104,"uid":9385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:21:31.000Z","msg":"人渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4e88bf667165cea7f37953ffe454f9bd4bc096","tid":264104,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:22:30.000Z","msg":"南亞？"},{"pid":"d3c4e24b258921296e8b96865a6375671d30534c","tid":264104,"uid":33572,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:23:36.000Z","msg":"大愛國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff236bb85b3de71554952fce2609c48fed05486","tid":264104,"uid":80015,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:26:01.000Z","msg":"扯左"},{"pid":"9561af4bfaadb9f85d3092cd88d570194988d2c1","tid":264104,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:27:28.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3febda7919302f5066cb12045c1c10de0b1c5e85","tid":264104,"uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:29:28.000Z","msg":"其實係報應嚟,鬼叫英國佬為咗錢將香港賣咗畀中國咩"},{"pid":"01035fa1d25506a053e0629f4daac1276de24aea","tid":264104,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:30:06.000Z","msg":"遣返去要切JJ？"},{"pid":"17391b339d6ecc25685dbaa37f93b94c531c7d2f","tid":264104,"uid":56729,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:36:06.000Z","msg":"訓左無睇<br />\n宜家難民隊係風化聯